      <title>摩根大通称英国央行降息空间“缩小”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-09/-narrower-wiggle-room-for-boe-rate-cuts-jpm-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩根大通全球经济学家诺拉·森蒂瓦尼 (Nora Szentivanyi) 讨论了英国经济形势，英镑跌至一年多以来的最低点，股市下跌，英国政府债券连续第四天下跌。森蒂瓦尼在彭博电视台发表讲话时表示，英国央行“近期可能还有进一步降息的空间”，但央行“越来越难以”对进一步降低利率到市场此前预期的水平抱有信心。（来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-09/-narrower-wiggle-room-for-boe-rate-cuts-jpm-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 09 Jan 2025 10:51:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国社会党领袖称预算妥协谈判取得进展</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-09/french-socialist-chief-says-talks-advancing-on-budget-compromise</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国社会党领袖奥利维尔·福尔表示，一些左翼政党与法国政府就预算问题的谈判正在取得进展，这为在法国总理弗朗索瓦·贝鲁下周公布其政策重点之前达成协议提供了潜在途径。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-09/french-socialist-chief-says-talks-advancing-on-budget-compromise</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 09 Jan 2025 10:14:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>波兰能源集团 Orlen 在业绩平淡的一年后提高 2035 年计划中的股息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-09/polish-energy-group-orlen-boosts-dividends-in-2035-plan-after-lackluster-year</link>
      <description><![CDATA[波兰最大的能源公司 Orlen SA 计划在未来十年增加股息并向清洁能源投资高达 910 亿美元，以在去年股价暴跌后重新赢得投资者的信心。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-09/polish-energy-group-orlen-boosts-dividends-in-2035-plan-after-lackluster-year</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 09 Jan 2025 09:59:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列官员在债券发售前在伦敦会见投资者</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-09/israel-officials-meet-investors-in-london-before-eurobond-sale</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，一群以色列政府官员本周将在伦敦与投资者会面，该国计划在第一季度发行欧元债券。由于会议是私下举行的，这些知情人士不愿透露姓名。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-09/israel-officials-meet-investors-in-london-before-eurobond-sale</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 09 Jan 2025 09:55:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国零售商股价因对经济的担忧加剧而下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-09/retailers-fall-hit-by-rising-investor-concerns-about-uk-economy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于人们对英国经济的担忧加剧以及工党增税预算的影响超过了假日季强劲的销售业绩，英国零售商股票遭遇抛售，特易购 (Tesco Plc) 和玛莎百货 (Marks &amp; Spencer Group Plc) 受到重创。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-09/retailers-fall-hit-by-rising-investor-concerns-about-uk-economy</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 09 Jan 2025 08:53:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国债券市场动荡令人回想起1976年债务危机</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-09/uk-bond-turmoil-gives-labour-nightmare-of-britain-s-1976-debt-crisis</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国最近的债券风暴让人联想到 2022 年利兹·特拉斯 (Liz Truss) 的迷你预算灾难，但将其与 20 世纪 70 年代的债务危机进行比较可能更为恰当。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-09/uk-bond-turmoil-gives-labour-nightmare-of-britain-s-1976-debt-crisis</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 09 Jan 2025 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>国债结束四天抛售；英国资产暴跌：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[受全球债券需求强劲信号的影响，美国国债本周首日上涨，结束了因投资者对政府债务和通胀上升的担忧而引发的抛售。英国资产继续遭受重创。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 Jan 2025 22:28:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>智利拒绝监管机构批准的 30 亿美元铁矿石项目</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/chile-dismisses-3-billion-iron-project-cleared-by-regulators-m5ogcj3j</link>
      <description><![CDATA[智利官员否决了一项采矿和港口项目，这是十多年来就一项 30 亿美元投资进行的法律和监管审议中出现的最新转折，该项目将环境保护与经济增长对立起来。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/chile-dismisses-3-billion-iron-project-cleared-by-regulators-m5ogcj3j</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 Jan 2025 22:09:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Codelco 利用债务市场为创纪录的铜矿支出提供资金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/codelco-taps-debt-market-to-fund-record-copper-mine-investments</link>
      <description><![CDATA[智利国有铜业公司 Codelco 发行了 15 亿美元债券，以筹集创纪录的投资，从而保持其作为全球最大铜生产商的地位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/codelco-taps-debt-market-to-fund-record-copper-mine-investments</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 Jan 2025 18:11:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Amundi、EDF 与多家公司联手要求欧盟不要削弱 ESG 规则</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/amundi-edf-among-firms-asking-eu-not-to-water-down-esg-rules</link>
      <description><![CDATA[包括 Amundi SA 和法国电力公司 (Electricite de France SA) 在内的一些法国最大的公司已签署了一封致欧洲政策制定者的信函，敦促他们确保欧盟坚持当前实施 ESG 报告规则的时间表。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/amundi-edf-among-firms-asking-eu-not-to-water-down-esg-rules</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 Jan 2025 16:57:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
